<h1>Our mission is to help people and businesses throughout the world realize their full potential. This drives our business and guides our corporate citizenship work.</h1>

<p>As the world’s largest software company, we help create social and economic opportunities wherever we work, live, and do business.</p>

<p>Our technology innovations, our people, our partnerships, and our day-to-day business make a meaningful contribution to the prosperity of communities and the sustainability of the planet.</p>

